/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.105254129757988e-43, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1096, \"end\": 1104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eventing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eventing\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eventing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eventing\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Ground Jury\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"Article\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"only official video recording\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"evidence\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In accordance with the rules, the Officials clarified at the Chef d'Equipes meeting prior to Cross Country that the fence camera footage would be the official video recording for the Cross Country test.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1276, \"end\": 1289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_of_athletics\", \"score\": 0.5741210725985463, \"rank\": 0.7416489885480347, \"text\": \"Cross Country\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_of_athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_of_athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 1366, \"end\": 1379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_of_athletics\", \"score\": 0.5741210725985463, \"rank\": 0.7416489885480347, \"text\": \"Cross Country\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_of_athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_of_athletics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"accordance\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"the Officials\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"the Chef d'Equipes meeting\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1266}, {\"ngram\": \"the fence camera footage\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1319}, {\"ngram\": \"the official video recording\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was the only footage that the Officials refer to for the purpose of making the decision.\\\"\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only footage\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"the Officials\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1430}, {\"ngram\": \"the purpose\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1455}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1478}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Without that penalty, the British team would have been 18.7 penalties ahead of France.\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1508, \"end\": 1515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9964115943028675, \"rank\": 0.002222669709283455, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1561, \"end\": 1567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9670016259001047, \"rank\": 0.02970911661235282, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that penalty\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"18.7 penalties\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead they had just 3.7.\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1595, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was just a bit sad like yesterday afternoon that that took up the whole day, really that there was no time to really appreciate the fantastic performance that the horse gave me and how much of a phenomenal cross-country horse he is, so I just think he should be celebrated for that,\\\" said Canter.\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1897, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"yesterday afternoon\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole day\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"no time\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1707}, {\"ngram\": \"the fantastic performance\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"the horse\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"a phenomenal cross-country horse\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"Canter\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But yeah, we put that behind us.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is sport: You win some, you lose some, but it wasn't on our side with the decision making.\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1945}, {\"ngram\": \"our side\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2001}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision making\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But you have to move on, and I really concentrated on getting the job done for the team today.\\\"\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The team wasn't perfect: Both Canter and Laura Collett (London 52) had a rail apiece, and Collett had 0.8-time penalties, but thanks to Tom McEwen's clear round with JL Dublin, the team finished on a 91.3 for their second consecutive gold medal.\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2166, \"end\": 2179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Collett\", \"score\": 0.9999948522786944, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Collett\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Collett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Collett\"}, {\"begin\": 2261, \"end\": 2271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_McEwen_(drag_racer)\", \"score\": 0.8873196584608332, \"rank\": 0.07814407814412813, \"text\": \"Tom McEwen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_McEwen_(drag_racer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_McEwen_(drag_racer)\"}, {\"begin\": 2291, \"end\": 2293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_Airlines\", \"score\": 0.9999999999845386, \"rank\": 1.5776099916936413e-11, \"text\": \"JL\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_Airlines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_Airlines\"}, {\"begin\": 2294, \"end\": 2300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_GAA\", \"score\": 0.9999999654510253, \"rank\": 3.454914669722884e-08, \"text\": \"Dublin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_GAA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_GAA\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The team\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2133}, {\"ngram\": \"Both Canter\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"London\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2187}, {\"ngram\": \"a rail\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2202}, {\"ngram\": \"Collett\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2222}, {\"ngram\": \"0.8-time penalties\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2310}, {\"ngram\": \"their second consecutive gold medal\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have said it a million times, but I can not say it enough: I owe everything to him.\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is my horse of a lifetime, and I am so, so proud of him,\\\" said Collett, who was the last to jump.\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my horse\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"a lifetime\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2487}, {\"ngram\": \"Collett\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was definitely not what we hoped for last night, but we managed to just think, 'Right, regroup; today is another day, another challenge,' and I guess it turns out we are all quite good under pressure, which is quite good.\\\"\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2786, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"last night\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2611}, {\"ngram\": \"Right, regroup\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2658}, {\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2665}, {\"ngram\": \"another day\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"another challenge\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2699}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Collett had the last fence down, which had fallen quite often throughout the day.\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Collett\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"the last fence\", \"from\": 2800, \"to\": 2814}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That meant she lost a little ground, moving into third individually.\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 2938, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little ground\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 2905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To be honest, I think the crowd \\u2026 maybe erupted slightly too early, but it was one of those fences [that] when you walked the course, you could not see it,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 3107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 2972}, {\"ngram\": \"those fences\", \"from\": 3027, \"to\": 3039}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It blended in, and it was a bit potluck whether it stayed up or not.\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not fault him.\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3200, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He jumped amazing, and it was good enough to win a team gold, so we will see what happens later.\\\"\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3298, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a team gold\", \"from\": 3250, \"to\": 3261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom McEwen, who was on the team in Tokyo, finished on his dressage score with JL Dublin, and the team finished on a total of 91.3.\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3300, \"end\": 3310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_McEwen_(drag_racer)\", \"score\": 0.8873196584608332, \"rank\": 0.07814407814412813, \"text\": \"Tom McEwen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_McEwen_(drag_racer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_McEwen_(drag_racer)\"}, {\"begin\": 3335, \"end\": 3340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.978977720739054e-13, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 3378, \"end\": 3380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_Airlines\", \"score\": 0.9999999999845386, \"rank\": 1.5776099916936413e-11, \"text\": \"JL\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_Airlines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_Airlines\"}, {\"begin\": 3381, \"end\": 3387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dublin_GAA\", \"score\": 0.9999999654510253, \"rank\": 3.454914669722884e-08, \"text\": \"Dubl