\"to\": 3676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was class from start to finish.\", \"from\": 3699, \"to\": 3733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"class\", \"from\": 3706, \"to\": 3711}, {\"ngram\": \"start\", \"from\": 3717, \"to\": 3722}, {\"ngram\": \"finish\", \"from\": 3726, \"to\": 3732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He jumped his socks off, and I knew it from the moment he warmed up, and he heard the crowd.\", \"from\": 3734, \"to\": 3826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his socks\", \"from\": 3744, \"to\": 3753}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 3788}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 3816, \"to\": 3825}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He really picked up.\\\"\", \"from\": 3827, \"to\": 3848, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While the French were close on the heels of Britain going into the day, all three of their riders, Nicolas Touzaint (Diabolo Menthe), Karim Florent Laghouag (Triton Fontaine) and Stephane Landois (Chaman Dumontceau) had rails to finish on 103.6 for the silver medal.\", \"from\": 3850, \"to\": 4116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3860, \"end\": 3866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8860564051209887, \"rank\": 0.12561328478831496, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3894, \"end\": 3901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9915239560274084, \"rank\": 0.00854516867911725, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3949, \"end\": 3965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Touzaint\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicolas Touzaint\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Touzaint\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Touzaint\"}, {\"begin\": 3967, \"end\": 3981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peppermint_Soda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Diabolo Menthe\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peppermint_Soda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peppermint_Soda\"}, {\"begin\": 3984, \"end\": 3989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karim_Wade\", \"score\": 0.9994078942023474, \"rank\": 0.0005923925757247091, \"text\": \"Karim\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karim_Wade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karim_Wade\"}, {\"begin\": 3990, \"end\": 3997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florent_Manaudou\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.709994425870528e-12, \"text\": \"Florent\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florent_Manaudou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florent_Manaudou\"}, {\"begin\": 4008, \"end\": 4014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Triton_motorcycle\", \"score\": 0.9993603013953637, \"rank\": 0.000373990637299233, \"text\": \"Triton\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Triton_motorcycle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Triton_motorcycle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the heels\", \"from\": 3881, \"to\": 3890}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 3913, \"to\": 3920}, {\"ngram\": \"their riders\", \"from\": 3935, \"to\": 3947}, {\"ngram\": \"Stephane Landois\", \"from\": 4029, \"to\": 4045}, {\"ngram\": \"Chaman Dumontceau\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4064}, {\"ngram\": \"rails\", \"from\": 4070, \"to\": 4075}, {\"ngram\": \"the silver medal\", \"from\": 4099, \"to\": 4115}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the third straight medal for the French, who won gold in Rio in 2016 and bronze in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 4117, \"to\": 4214, \"entities\":